                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5418" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0070</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9248 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">拼多多的扶贫之路：社会责任与商业模式的融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Pinduoduo&#39;s road to poverty alleviation: integration of social responsibility and business model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">游晓东，王韬越，刘党文，葛彦辰，尹婷，严雪玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">拼多多（上海）网络科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> 14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电商企业；社会责任；精准扶贫；商业价值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">E-commerce enterprises;social responsibility;targeted poverty alleviation；commercial value</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">传统的电商企业在“新消费”的时代背景下正在不断转变。拼多多作为其中一随着时代发展，越来越多的企业开始重视社会责任的承担。有些人认为承担社会责任能够给企业带来隐形优势，但是相反的，从股东价值最大化的角度看，也有许多人认为这将损害股东权益。拼多多作为一家平台型企业，积极响应国家精准扶贫政策，结合自身商业模式走出了一条独特的扶贫助农之路。拼多多将电商平台、农户、企业以及政府相结合，以农产品销售为切入点来实现扶贫助农。那么，这种社会责任与商业模式相融合的做法，给拼多多带来的是机遇还是危机呢？本案例将详细描述拼多多以农产品为主要切入点对口帮扶贫困农村地区的过程，并结合拼多多自身商业模式对其扶贫模式进行了系统的归纳总结，希望能够为有意愿履行社会责任的电商企业提供经验及启发。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the development of the times, enterprises pay more and more attention to social responsibility. Some people think that social responsibility can bring invisible advantages to enterprises, but on the contrary, from the perspective of maximizing shareholder value, it will damage shareholders&#39; rights and interests. As a platform enterprise, pinduoduo actively responds to the national policy of targeted poverty alleviation, and combines with its own business model to find a unique way to help the poor and farmers. Pinduoduo combines the e-commerce platform, farmers, enterprises and the government, and takes the sales of agricultural products as the breakthrough point to achieve poverty alleviation. So, is the integration of social responsibility and business model an opportunity or a crisis for pinduoduo? This case will describe in detail the process of pinduoduo helping poor rural areas with agricultural products as the main marketing point, and systematically summarize its poverty alleviation mode, hoping to provide experience and inspiration for e-commerce enterprises willing to fulfill their social responsibilities.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《企业社会责任》、《商业模式》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">扶贫、社会责任、商业模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-06</td>
                            </tr>
